OL,5,G0055 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,6,     FUndercover detectives Steve and
OL,7,     FAdam overhear two people
OL,8,     Fdiscussing what they have just
OL,9,     Fshoplifted. The team go in pursuit
OL,10,     Fbut the suspected stolen goods are
OL,11,     Fnowhere to be seen. (Ep4)
OL,12,G0155 Outback Truckers
OL,13,     FSteve and dog Bella are in a race
OL,14,     Facross the red deserts of
OL,15,     FAustralia hauling classic cars to
OL,16,     Fauction but delays in loading and
OL,17,     Fthe arrival of the wet season
OL,18,     Fthreaten the journey home.
